Hello all-

EndlessForms.com was announced by Cornell today.

Wesley put it on Hacker News, please help by "upvoting".

http://news.ycombinator.com/newest

Our story is called: "Breed 3-D Printable Objects, No Technical Know-How
Needed"

Here is another, longer article:

http://www.physorg.com/news/2011-08-endless-web-d-printable.html

Please help spread the word!

Best regards,
Jeff Clune

Postdoctoral Fellow
Hod Lipson's Creative Machines Lab
Cornell University
jeffclune@...
jeffclune.com <http://jeffclune.com>
